00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:14,240
Mr. Tang,

905
00:41:15,250 --> 00:41:16,650
I want to find Chuanxiang

906
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:18,480
and ask him

907
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:20,690
